   <descr>
      <p>"Laughter in the Rain" is a song recorded by Neil Sedaka and
    written by Sedaka and Phil Cody. It hit number one on the
    Billboard Hot 100 on February 1, 1975. The song also spent two
    weeks atop the adult contemporary chart.</p>
      <p>This song was covered by Thomas Anders (of Modern Talking
    fame) in 1992 for his album 
    <i>Down on Sunset</i>. It was also covered by Pepe Jaramillo on
    his 
    <i>Mexican Tijuana / Mexican Gold</i>album.</p>
